para.para.body:
The property 
                     S^{\bot} = \span(S)^{\bot}
                  .   We read this as:

We know that 
                     S
                   is contained in 
                     \span(S)
                  . So we see that 
                     \span(S)^{\bot}
                   is contained in 
                     S^{\bot}
                   from the previous property. That 
                     S^{\bot}
                   is also contained in 
                     \span(S)^{\bot}
                   requires proof by computation.
